** Configuring and Invoking LTC Mode

  Before you can use LTC, you must start the base system first.  See {{{./usage.html}Usage}} for more details.  Now you should be able to invoke LTC from Emacs using <<<M-x ltc-mode>>>.

  If you need to customize LTC, for example to change the port number, start the base system with option <<<-p <PORT>>>:

+---
$ java -jar LTC-all-0.9-SNAPSHOT.jar -p 5555
